title: Walking.With.Dinosaurs.S02E03.Passing.of.Giants.WS.DSR.XviD-K4RM
description:
Walking.With.Dinosaurs.S02E03.Passing.of.Giants.WS.DSR.XviD-K4RM4

In this continuation of the story of our past we look at the causes that brought about the end of the large dinosaurs and explain why some survived and why others passed into the fossils of time.

Using new evidence and modern day science we can show you in a way never seen till this series a new and unique way of seeing and understanding the life of dinosaurs.
